    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "As discussed with @alexandraB99, we are commonly using `available` size, there comes a binding loop: \r\n```\r\nimplicitWidth \r\n> contentWidth \r\n > contentItem.childrenRect.width \r\n  > availableWidth \r\n   > width \r\n    > implicitWidth\r\n```\r\n\r\nSo it's fine to add `implicit` sizes to `StatusScrollView`, as far as we don't add any binding loops.",
